    <h1>Dryer Vent Installation Cost in Los Angeles &amp; Orange County</h1>

    <p>A properly installed dryer vent is a fire safety requirement — the US Fire Administration reports that clogged or improperly installed dryer vents cause over 2,900 residential fires annually. Same Day Appliance Repair installs, replaces, and reroutes dryer vents throughout Los Angeles County, Orange County, and Ventura County. Licensed, same-day service — we handle everything from a simple vent replacement to complex reroutes through walls and ceilings.</p>

